description:
Oceans of Time is the seventh studio album by German heavy metal guitarist Axel Rudi Pell, released in September 1998 on Steamhammer Records. 

Oceans of Time is the first Pell album to feature vocalist Johnny Gioeli and keyboardist Ferdy Doernberg, both of whom still perform with Pell as of 2013.
